definition: special/unique/distinguished/especially/unusual/very/abbr. for 特克斯[te4 ke4 si1], tex
to set/to fix/to determine/to decide/to order

sentences.english: You work on your muscle groups in a certain order.
sentences.chinese: 对各个肌肉群，你是在按照一个特定的顺序进行。

sentences.english: Dreyman: I specifically said no books.
sentences.chinese: 特定的我提醒过不要书。

sentences.english: A limitation of the analysis was that population-specific effects were not considered.
sentences.chinese: 这项分析的限制是并未考虑到族群特定的效应。

sentences.english: You are already too locked in to a vendor-specific standard.
sentences.chinese: 已经受到特定供应商的标准的太多约束。

sentences.english: It is the representative power of the villagers' representatives that forms the specific basis of the village.
sentences.chinese: 正是村民代表的代表能力构成了特定的村庄基础。

sentences.english: In a larger company, you would assign these roles to specific user groups.
sentences.chinese: 在较大的公司中，会将这些角色分配给特定的用户组。

sentences.english: Racial feats are available only to characters of a specific race.
sentences.chinese: 种族专长仅适用于人物的特定种族。

sentences.english: Provides recommendations for using device-specific templates supported by mobile controls.
sentences.chinese: 提供使用行动控制项支援的装置特定样板的建议。

sentences.english: This difference has a special influence to the form of paper sheet.
sentences.chinese: 这个差别对纸页的形成具有特定的影响。

sentences.english: It does not tie itself to one particular transport.
sentences.chinese: 它并没有将自己绑定在某种特定传输方式上。

sentences.english: Search for a specific file type.
Any waste liquid or material shall be handled per the specific plant procedure.
sentences.chinese: 任何废液或废物料要根据全厂特定程序进行处理。

sentences.english: A seemingly inflexible adherence to specific, nonfunctional routines or rituals
sentences.chinese: 僵化地坚持某些特定，非功能性的生活习惯或仪式。

sentences.english: The answer was to block certain estuaries leading to Antwerp and Rotterdam
sentences.chinese: 答案是阻塞一些特定的通往安特卫普和鹿特丹的河口。

sentences.english: The data will be used for specific purposes only, and all indentifiable information would be discarded after the conference.
sentences.chinese: 这些资料只用作特定的用途，并于活动完结后销毁。

sentences.english: This code can be followed by a reference to a specific account.
sentences.chinese: 这个代码后面可以跟一个对一个特定账户的引用。

definition: to correspond/answering (one another)/to agree (among the part)/corresponding/relevant/appropriate/(modify) accordingly
in simple terms/to put things simply/briefly
